Package: obisrecipes
Title: Visualization and Mapping Tools for OBIS Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Silas", family = "Principe", email = "s.principe@unesco.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8059-6304")),
    person(given = "OBIS Secretariat", email = "helpdesk@obis.org", role = "aut"))
Description: A curated collection of reusable visualization and mapping
    functions for data from the Ocean Biodiversity Information System
    (OBIS, <https://obis.org>). Provides ggplot2 themes and colorblind-safe
    color scales tailored for marine data, static world basemaps with
    bathymetry and species occurrence layers, and interactive WebGL maps
    via 'mapgl' including a DeckGL H3 hexagon widget. Intended primarily
    for internal use by the OBIS Secretariat and OBIS nodes.
